### Get All Doctors
GET http://localhost:5000/api/doctors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Doctor by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/doctors/DOCTOR_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create Doctor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/doctors
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_id": "USER_ID_HERE",
    "specialization": "Cardiology",
    "qualification": ["MBBS", "MD"],
    "department_id": "DEPARTMENT_ID_HERE",
    "shift": "Morning",
    "working_hours": "9AM-5PM",
    "availability_status": true
}

### Get Daily Schedule
GET http://localhost:5000/api/doctors/schedule/daily?doctor_id=DOCTOR_ID_HERE&date=2024-03-20
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Weekly Schedule
GET http://localhost:5000/api/doctors/schedule/weekly?doctor_id=DOCTOR_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE 